      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Abu Ali Al Ashary, from Muhammad Bin Abdul Jabbar, from Safwan, from Is’haq Bin Ammar, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Al-Hassan<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The fabricator would be whipped with a whipping between the two whippings. All of his body would be whipped’."
